---
title: Buttery Herb and Garlic Turkey Dinner with Balsamic Brussels Sprouts and Parmesan Mash
description: Inspired by comfort food favourite, pot pie, this feast doesn't miss a beat. Garlic-butter pulls double duty in both the herb roasted turkey, as well as the creamy Parmesan mash. Tangy balsamic Brussels sprouts bring bright flavours, and the finisher is a velvety cream sauce.
